\c 31
\s Kufa kwaSauro nekukundwa kweVaIsraeri paGibhoa
\p
\v 1 Zvino VaFirisitia vakarwa naIsraeri, varume VaIsraeri ndokutiza pamberi peVaFirisitia, vakawa vafa pagomo reGiribhoa.
\v 2 VaFirisitia ndokunamatira pana Sauro nepavanakomana vake. VaFirisitia ndokuuraya Jonatani naAbhinadhabi naMarikishua vanakomana vaSauro.
\v 3 Zvino hondo yakaomera Sauro, vafuri ndokumuwana, varume veuta, zvino akarwadziswa zvikuru nevafuri.
\v 4 Zvino Sauro wakati kumutakuri wezvombo zvake: Vhomora munondo wako ugondibvarura nawo, zvimwe ava vasina kudzingiswa varege kusvika vandibaye, nokundidadira. Asi mubati wenhumbi dzake dzokurwa nadzo wakaramba, nokuti wakange achitya kwazvo. Naizvozvo Sauro akatora munondo wake, akazviwisira pauri.
\v 5 Zvino mubati wenhumbi dzake dzokurwa nadzo wakati achiona kuti Sauro wafa, naiye akazviwisira pamunondo wakewo, akafa pamwe chete naye.
\v 6 Naizvozvo Sauro akafa, pamwe chete navanakomana vake vatatu, nomubati wenhumbi dzake dzokurwa nadzo, navanhu vake vese nomusi iwoyo.
\p
\v 7 Zvino vanhu VaIsraeri, vakange vari mhiri komupata, navakange vachiona kuti vanhu VaIsraeri vatiza, uye kuti Sauro navanakomana vake vakange vafawo, vakabva pamaguta, vakatiza; VaFirisitia vakasvika, vakagaramo.
\v 8 Zvino fume mangwana VaFirisitia vakati vachiuya kuzokusunungura vakaurawa, vakawana Sauro navanakomana vake vatatu vafa pagomo reGiribhoa.
\v 9 Vakagura musoro wake, nokusunungura nhumbi dzake dzokurwa nadzo, vakatuma nhume kumativi ese enyika yaVaFirisitia, kundozivisa mashoko iwayo kuimba yezvifananidzo zvavo, nokuvanhu.
\v 10 Vakaisa nhumbi dzake dzokurwa nadzo mumba yavaAshitaroti, vakasungira chitunha chake pamadziro eBhetishani.
\p
\v 11 Zvino vakange vagere JabheshiGiriyadhi vakati vachinzwa zvakange zvaitirwa Sauro naVaFirisitia,
\v 12 mhare dzese dzikasimuka, dzikafamba usiku hwese, dzikatora chitunha chaSauro nezvitunha zvavanakomana vake pamadziro eBhetishani, vakaenda Jabheshi vakazvipisapo.
\v 13 Vakatora mafupa avo, vakaaviga pasi pomuti womutamarisiki paJabheshi, vakatsanya mazuva manomwe.
